genresAdvancedInfo.name: north alabama indie
genresAdvancedInfo.description: North Alabama Indie is a subgenre of indie rock that originated in the northern region of Alabama. It is characterized by its raw, gritty sound and DIY ethos, often incorporating elements of folk, blues, and country music. North Alabama Indie bands often prioritize authenticity and storytelling in their lyrics, drawing inspiration from the region's rich musical history.
